# ------------------------------------------------------------
# SQL Server Elite DBA Project – Git ignore rules
# ------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. Keep secrets out of source control
# 2. Ignore IDE / OS temp files
# 3. Ignore local tooling artifacts
# ------------------------------------------------------------

# ─── Docker Compose override files (contain passwords) ──────
# Each developer keeps their own override with secrets.
**/*override.yml

# ─── Performance Monitor binary logs ─────────────────────────
*.blg

# ─── OS / Editor noise ──────────────────────────────────────
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
~$*

# ─── Python / Node cache (if added later) ───────────────────
__pycache__/
node_modules/
